      <p>The ten <strong>Heavenly Stems</strong> cycle through five elements in Yin-Yang pairs. The twelve <strong>Earthly Branches</strong> correspond to the twelve <a href="/zodiac/">zodiac animals</a> and carry hidden elemental content.</p>
